				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">&quot;Second V register&quot; is the solution adopted by the ColecoVision, MSX, and Master System, not the NES. The correct solution for the NES is just to skip setting <em>v = t</em> on the prerender line if rendering is turned off.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

